=Episode 14=

20
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:17,480
Miss Song, I don't think you come

21
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:19,280
to bring me any good news.

22
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,640
Not at all, Mr. Leng.

23
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:23,160
I want to see Nanchen tonight.

24
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:23,880
But lately,

25
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:26,480
he's annoyed for losing the contract
with Song's Group

26
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,520
and doesn't want to see me.

27
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:28,880
I wonder

28
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:30,160
if you can do something about it.

29
