Miss Song, do you think

30
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:36,920
I have to solve your boring love problem

31
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,160
simply because you know my secret?

32
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:41,520
Mr. Leng, you exaggerated it.

33
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:42,960
Don't be too nervous.

34
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:45,360
